Louis: 17 yrs. old. A normal youth with ordinary interests.
Hildebrand Francis Longford: 18 yrs. old. Hildegarde's older brother.
Charles: 16 yrs old. A true merryman.

Hildegarde Joan Longford: 16 yrs. old. She's nice enough.
Margaret: 16 yrs. old. Too much indoors.
Phyllis: 16 yrs. old. Could use some restraint.

